<HEADLINE>
<P>
AYATOLLAH KHOMEINI AND 'THE SATANIC VERSES' 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
We have been reading in our daily newspapers about Muslim fundamentalists 
demanding that America ban "The Satanic Verses." It has only been a few months 
since similar Christian fundamentalists were calling for the banning of the 
movie "The Last Temptation of Christ" right here in California. 
</P>
<P>
I think that both Christian fundamentalism and Muslim fundamentalism are two 
sides of the same dangerous coin. If it were up to these religious experts on 
everything, we would know nothing about real history, astronomy, organic 
evolution, or rationalism. 
</P>
<P>
ALAN ALBERT SNOW 
</P>
<P>
Santa Ana 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Letter to the Editor 
</P>
</TYPE>
