<HEADLINE>
<P>
ELLIOTT'S PAC-10 MARK SHOULD GET AN ASTERISK 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
While I agree that Sean Elliott is quite a basketball player and scoring 
machine, it would logically appear to me that either he, Reggie Miller and the 
other top Pac-10 scorers should have an asterisk by their records, or Lew 
Alcindor should have one. 
</P>
<P>
Alcindor made his record in three seasons, while the others took four. 
</P>
<P>
Fair is fair. 
</P>
<P>
RON SEERY 
</P>
<P>
Los Angeles 
</P>
