Fremont's Louis Austin, left, in a City 3-A semifinal. ; Photo, Jason Farrell, 
center, of El Camino Real applies defensive pressure in the Conquistadores' 
66-63 playoff loss to Fremont. LAWRENCE K. HO / Los Angeles Times; Photo, 
Senior Brent Lofton posted 34 points and 15 rebounds in a losing effort. CARLOS 
CHAVEZ / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
