off the Pioneers' title bid with a 2-0 upset in a Southern Section 4-A 
quarterfinal. ; Photo, Craig Hampton, right, screens out Hawthorne goalie Dana 
Lindleman, but Simi Valley failed to score. GEORGE WILHELM / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
