<HEADLINE>
<P>
CRUISE AND QUAYLE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
I was enormously insulted by Greg Morrison's suggestion that Tom Cruise 
obviously accounts for the popularity of "Rain Man" with female audience 
