<HEADLINE>
<P>
MOROCCO INMATES MUTINY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
From Reuters 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
RABAT, Morocco 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Several people were hospitalized after clashes between prisoners and guards 
during a mutiny that ended Friday in Rabat's overcrowded El Alou prison, 
officials said. Lawyers said there are more than 1,800 inmates in the prison, 
which was built for 400. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
